# elants_spi touch controller: keep runtime PM on.
# Runtime-suspend disables the touch IRQ and sends the controller to idle;
# the driver's resume path does not reliably bring it back to scan mode
# (observed: controller stops reporting touches entirely until manually
# poked). Pin it active — the panel's touch scan draw is negligible next to
# the display engine.
ACTION=="add", SUBSYSTEM=="spi", DRIVERS=="elants_spi", ATTR{power/control}="on"
